long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Time Analytics allows users to track and analyze their website usage. With this extension, you can see exactly how much time you spend on each website on a daily basis, giving you valuable insights into your online habits. Whether you're looking to boost productivity or just want to gain a better understanding of your digital footprint, Time Analytics is the perfect tool to help you do so. With its easy-to-use interface and detailed reporting, you can make better use of your time online and achieve your goals more effectively.
